br><br>Well, i think you should play what you WANT to play.. many hardcore paladin probably get mad and saying that cant be.. ranger not that good.. Well, whatever.. this is been tested and proven.. Paladin just not good on dealing damage to enemy/is. Ranger finish up mobs good and fast.. Paladin got superior heal and rez, ranger got DDs. Play what you want :)<br><br>PS: 47 ranger ABLE to solo hill giant (snare and shoot DD shoot finished up with melee require about 300arrows) As for me (60paly), i tried to solo giant before.. end up forced to root it and zoned out.. so dont try this at home :) (holy forge sucks!) :)</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >1 Replies</td></tr></table><table width="100%"><tr><td class=mhback>&nbsp;</td><td class=mhback >Thread Subject</a></td><td class=mhback>Started by</a></td><td class=mhback>Replies</a></td><td class=mhback>Last Post</a></td><td class=mhback>Rating</a></td></tr><tr class=mdr>
